    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " This was given by Paul as a sign unto them of the truth of what he had said, which, when it came to pass, might induce them to believe the rest; which probably it did, and saved Paul from being killed by the soldiers, ",
        "children": []
