            "text": "Acts 27:42",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Thus God preserves his people, and delivers Paul, and brings all his safely off at the last, but it is by tempests and storms. It may be they must suffer shipwreck of all they have in this world first. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Augusta per angusta.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Through many tribulations we must enter into the kingdom of God, as St. Paul had taught others, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Acts 14:22",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
